text: Gustav Collin (23 May 1890 - 25 October 1966) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Male freestyle swimmers
